               <lb ed="#T" n="31" type="fixed=27"/>DIVISIO PRIME PARTIS 
      <lb ed="#T" n="32"/>TEXTVS. 
      <lb ed="#T" n="33"/>APostolus namque &amp;c.] Postquam ostendit 
      <lb ed="#T" n="34"/>Avnitatem, &amp; Trinitatem per scripturas, 
      <lb ed="#T" n="35"/>hic probat per creaturas. Et primo probat 
      vni<lb ed="#T" n="36" break="no"/>tatem per se, per rationes naturales. Secundo 
      <lb ed="#T" n="37"/>Trinitatem per se per vestigium 
      creatura<lb ed="#T" n="38" break="no"/>rum. [Nunc restat] Tertio vnitatem &amp; 
      Trinita<lb ed="#T" n="39" break="no"/>tem simul, per imaginem creaturarum 
      rationa<lb ed="#T" n="40" break="no"/>bilium. [Nunc vero ad eam. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="pdt7y6-ee6691-d1e715">
               <lb ed="#T" n="41"/>In prima parte probat unitatem per quatuor.  
      <lb ed="#T" n="42"/>rationes, quarum prima sumitur a creaturarum. 
      <lb ed="#T" n="43"/>magnitudine: secunda a creaturarum 
      mutabili<lb ed="#T" n="44" break="no"/>tate. [Alio etiam modo] Tertia a creaturarum. 
      <lb ed="#T" n="45"/>differenti. bonitate. [Considerauerunt &amp;c. 
      <lb ed="#T" n="46"/>Quarta a creaturarum speciositate. [
      Intel<lb ed="#T" n="47" break="no"/>lexerunt &amp;c. ] Prima penes causam 
      efficien<lb ed="#T" n="48" break="no"/>tem secunda penes materialem; ex qua 
      <lb ed="#T" n="49"/>inest mutabilitas; tertia penes causam finalem; 
      <lb ed="#T" n="50"/>quarta penes causam formalem: Per primam 
      <lb ed="#T" n="51"/>ostenditur omni potentia Dei; per secundam 
      <lb ed="#T" n="52"/>aeternitas Dei; per tertiam summa bonitas Dei; 
      <lb ed="#T" n="53"/>per quartam summa sapientia Dei. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="pdt7y6-ee6691-d1e747">
               <lb ed="#T" n="54"/>[Nunc restat. ] In hac secunda parte 
      princi<lb ed="#T" n="55" break="no"/>pali primo ostendit, qualiter est vestigium 
      Tri<lb ed="#T" n="56" break="no"/>nitatis in creaturis: secundo qualiter per illud 
      <lb ed="#T" n="57"/>cognoscatur Trinitas Creatoris [In illa enim 
      <lb ed="#T" n="58"/>Trinitate summa] Tertio ostendit 
      imperfe<lb ed="#T" n="59" break="no"/>ctionem huius cognitionis. [Ecce ostensum. 
    </p>
